## 🛡️ Risk Mitigation & Recommended Controls
To reduce the risk of a successful incident via removable media, the following multi-layered controls are recommended:

| Control Type | Implementation Strategy | Impact |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Managerial** | [cite_start]Implement employee awareness programs regarding suspicious peripherals[cite: 2]. | Reduces human susceptibility to "lost USB" baits. |
| **Operational** | [cite_start]Establish routine antivirus and malware scans for all external devices[cite: 2]. | Detects known signatures before execution. |
| **Technical** | [cite_start]Disable **AutoPlay/AutoRun** via Group Policy on all company PCs[cite: 2]. | Prevents the automatic execution of malicious code. |



